731
01:04:43,379 --> 01:04:45,648
It's a problem, a halachic problem.

732
01:04:48,885 --> 01:04:51,954
Strange, this problem was picked up

733
01:04:51,954 --> 01:04:53,856
in the Torah

734
01:04:55,258 --> 01:04:57,159
in Bechukosai.

735
01:04:57,159 --> 01:05:00,663
In the parshah which 
we just read last Shabbos.

736
01:05:03,099 --> 01:05:06,202
There is a strange pasuk in Bechukosai.

737
01:05:06,202 --> 01:05:07,737
"V'nasasi es

