01:06:21,577 --> 01:06:24,547
Interpretation number one,

754
01:06:26,615 --> 01:06:31,387
your sanctuaries will be in a
state of desolation, 

755
01:06:34,623 --> 01:06:40,329
which -- and in consequence, 
